{"tid":2379600,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生疑攬警為救兩少女 被控阻差辦公 辯方質疑警員夾口供","createTime":"2021-01-25T10:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:14:20.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fba292d150b9176929c32f9d477cd614fd64bbd9","tid":2379600,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"當晚有防暴警追捕兩名黑衣少女時，疑遭一名中六男學生出手阻攔，防暴警與隊員遂改為拘捕男生。男生被控阻差辦公罪，案件今在屯門法院開審。聲稱受阻的警員供稱，在馬路上追捕人群隊尾的兩名女子時，突感到有人伸手攬他，回頭看見被告在行人路逃走。惟辯方指警員與兩名同袍的書面口供，就查問<span class=\"red\">被告位置所在的門牌號碼一事犯下同一錯誤，質疑三人事前夾口供</span>；警員否認。<br />\n<br />\n李姓被告男生（17歲）否認一項阻撓警務人員罪，控罪指他於去年3月22日凌晨在元朗又新街與合益路交界犯案，故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員、即<span class=\"red\">警員24004李文軒</span>。<br />\n<br />\n警員與兩名追截同袍的書面口供均同樣寫錯同一個門牌號碼，三份口供中提及的位置與警員庭上所說的位置有出入。辯方質疑，能夠出現如此錯誤，是因警員與兩名同袍在錄口供前曾經「夾口供」所致。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員的<span class=\"red\">書面紀錄沒提到有否向被告解釋拘捕罪名及被告有否在警誡下回應</span>，質疑學堂是否教他應記錄查問的所有程序。警員辯稱「冇話一字一句都要記錄」、「已經寫咗宣佈拘捕，已經夠」。辯方指現時沒有紀錄顯示警員曾否做過相關程序，<span class=\"red\">警員回應稱：「咁冇紀錄囉依家。」</span>"},{"pid":"ca98940f533374d4182336f726b8cdef231de922","tid":2379600,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/NF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FNF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=033334b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FNF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M%2F&h=073005bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/NF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M/</a>"},{"pid":"2f6dedb60e6562eb2ebf49099c3b8eeefd9d696e","tid":2379600,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ad56145537af2ac24b8a2cf10fc7c4670f91c5","tid":2379600,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"警員與兩名追截同袍的書面口供均同樣寫錯同一個門牌號碼，三份口供中提及的位置與警員庭上所說的位置有出入。辯方質疑，能夠出現如此錯誤，是因警員與兩名同袍在錄口供前曾經「夾口供」所致。"},{"pid":"35edcf78197cee4421cd6a49e7a6f10445c0a963","tid":2379600,"uid":273157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca98940f533374d4182336f726b8cdef231de922","tid":2379600,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/NF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FNF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=033334b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FNF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M%2F&h=073005bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/NF5ZBICSR5D6BCCX4MM5N65Y2M/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"警員 李文軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd3b6dff3f44ec5270d35544d02eb88e39c7dc1","tid":2379600,"uid":126317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"現實版英雄救美 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd14e1ef9315da1ba931148c2e59d106d609003","tid":2379600,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883fb934e4e8ae6cb9fc31283f331f